title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 11/10/2018
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 11/10/2018
description:
Coming off a 4-1 week Colin gives his Blazing 5 picks to RJ Bell of pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio and RJ tells him which ones the wise guys in Vegas agree and disagree with. Plus, Colin reveals a bonus pick that was not included in his original Blazing 5.
